  <brief_title>Juvenile Postlumbar Puncture Headache After Puncture With Needles With Quincke Tip or With Sprotte Tip</brief_title>
  <official_title>Postlumbar Puncture Complaints After Lumbar Punctures in Children and Adolescents: Frequency and Impact by Compariosn of Two Needle Designs</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Heidelberg University</agency>
